episodes.title: Whoopi Goldberg Explains WHY Her Name Is in the Epstein Files
episodes.description: 'The View' host Whoopi Goldberg explains why her name appears in the Epstein files, which were made public by the Department of Justice in January. 'The View' airs weekdays on ABC.

episodes.title: RHOSLC: Mary Cosby's Co-Stars DEFEND Her From Cult Allegations (Exclusive)
episodes.description: Mary Cosby, Angie Katsanevas and Bronwyn Newport chat with ET's Brice Sander at BravoCon 2025 in Las Vegas. 'The Real Housewives of Salt Lake City' co-stars react to all the drama that went down during the show's 'Below Deck: Down Under' crossover including Britani's unicorn, Angie breaking her finger and the infamous flight back home. Plus, Angie and Bronwyn defend Mary against accusations she running a cult with her husband.

episodes.title: Leah Remini Mourns Mike Rinder, Scientology and the Aftermath Co-Host, Dead at 69
episodes.description: Leah Remini remembers her 'Scientology and the Aftermath' co-host, Mike Rinder, who died Sunday, in a lengthy tribute on X. He was 69. The friends and former Scientology members also shared a podcast together, 'Fair Game.'
